  T:products=[B0DCK8P752=steam,B09CP8SSGP=dryer]
  T:add_new_product⇒add_to_PRODUCTS_list+add_html_markers|no_workflow_change
  T:rate_limit=2s_between_requests
  A:expose_api_key_in_html_or_js⇒absolute_forbidden
  A:commit_if_price_unchanged⇒skip
  A:hardcode_price_without_marker⇒forbidden|must_use_data-price_span



